- adjust the diagrams of built-in workflows.

Steps to replicate
# Navigate to send email page (g + g + send E-mail)
# Select a group or project roles
# Put the following subject: {{#if( !$foo )  <strong>this is it</strong> #end}}
# Write something in the body
# Message type can be either html or text
# Click Send and check the email received.
